Name: Kareem Washington
Description:
Kareem was stabbed several times in the back and throat.

> When found by two employees of a nearby trucking company, Washington, who was wearing women's clothing, had been stabbed several times in the back and throat. Washington had been seen alive near
the area around 6:00 a.m. on Monday, approximately four hours before the body was discovered.
>
> Police do not yet have a suspect or a murder weapon, but they don't believe robbery was the motive, as Washington's wallet, containing both cash and identification, was found on the body.
>
> The area where Washington's body was found, Hanover Street, is also known as a haven for sex work. Washington's mother, Cynthia Washington, is adamant that her child was not a sex worker, as investigators have theorized.

*Courtesy of Gender Advocacy Network News and The Bergen Record, 1999*
